<section class="section howtobegin">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-2"></div>
        <div class="col-lg-7">
            <h1 class="text-center ql-font-serif">
                <br />
                <b>How To Begin With CV Sharer?</b>
                <br />
                <br />
            </h1>

            <p style="font-size:1.25rem">You can follow the easy steps and create your own customized professional CV with CVSharer for free now!</p>

            <h3>
                <b>
                    <br />
                    Step 1: Create Your CVSharer Account
                </b>
            </h3>

            <p style="font-size:1.25rem"> <br />✔ You can create your CVSharer account by clicking the register button shown below.</p>
            <p>
