                    <img src="~/assets/img/register_ss3.png"  />
                </div>    
            </p>

            <p style="font-size:1.25rem"> <br />✔ Now you have a CVSharer account! Let's continue with the next step!</p>

            <h3>
                <b>
                    <br />
                    Step 2: Add Your CV Information To Your Account
                </b>
            </h3>

            <p style="font-size:1.25rem"> <br />✔ You can navigate to your profile page with clicking to "My Profile" button under your profile.</p>
            <p>
                <div style="text-align: center;">
                    <img src="~/assets/img/profile_ss.png"  />
                </div>    
            </p>
            
